blog.name: weirdandwackypokefusions
blog.title: Well that's strange!
blog.description:
Welcome!  I create, using the all-mighty classic Microsoft XP Paint, my own pokemon fusions. All the sprites come from pokestadium and usually people on deviantart/ the xy/sun&moon sprite project. I don't own any of the sprite used, I just fuse them! 
REQUESTS ARE OPEN! Ask Box: 3/15.
PLEASE FEEL FREE TO DRAW MY FUSIONS!!  I absolutely love it when people draw them! There's no need to ask either! Just make sure you tag me so them I can see it!
I hope you enjoy my fusions!

summary: So, I saw these 3 fusions and I fell in love with them and wanted to make sprites of them.   I absolutely love the little cloak...
caption:
So, I saw these 3 fusions and I fell in love with them and wanted to make sprites of them.  

I absolutely love the little cloak on the ampharos/tropius fusion. It was just so cute. Also drew a banana for it as well. Fusion by @shusheries and can be found here: https://shusheries.tumblr.com/post/177603495148/he-sorta-looks-like-a-little-rogue-or-something

The absol/raikou fusion looks really awesome and I love the patterns on its body. Not gonna lie, was a pain to get the head looking right.  Fusion made by @theemeraldotter and can be found here: http://theemeraldotter.tumblr.com/day/2018/08/30. 

And the drifblim/tyrunt fusion looks really cool and I love how it incorporates each part of each pokemon. Fusion by @endlesspokemonfusion and can be found here: https://endlesspokemonfusion.tumblr.com/post/177590590562/drifblim-x-tyrunt-pokemon-fusion. This person needs more likes and reblogs and stuff because their art is awesome and I love their fusions! 

Go check these guys out because their art is amazing!
